{"title":"Yeti Cycles Commemorates its 40th Anniversary with a Limited Edition ASR","link":"https://theradavist.com/yeti-cycles-40th-anniversary-asr/","date":1743693839000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/40th_Yeti_Cycles_ASR.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/40th_Yeti_Cycles_ASR.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/40th_Yeti_Cycles_ASR.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/40th_Yeti_Cycles_ASR.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Fifteen years ago, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/yeti-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Yeti Cycles</a> created the brand’s first ever ‘Anniversary’ bike to celebrate its brand heritage. And since, it’s become a tradition to celebrate big birthdays with a bike that honors its history with one of the Colorado-based brand’s current models. This 40th anniversary ASR is a bike inspired by the history of Yeti Cycles, but more importantly, the people who shaped the sport…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Top-Tube.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Top-Tube.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Top-Tube.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Top-Tube.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_SP-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_SP-Badge.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_SP-Badge.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_SP-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>40th Anniversary ASR Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>MAP $13,000</li>\n<li>115 mm rear travel</li>\n<li>130 mm fork travel</li>\n<li>66.1º head angle</li>\n<li>T-Series Wireless Frame</li>\n<li>Custom 40th Anniversary paint scheme</li>\n<li>Special Projects Limited Edition numbered frames “X/200”</li>\n<li>28-36t Max (38t MD-XL) chainring compatibility</li>\n<li>2 main frame water bottles</li>\n<li>Custom FOX Factory 34 SL GripX 130mm</li>\n<li>Custom DT Swiss XMC1200 wheelset</li>\n<li>Custom SRAM XX components</li>\n<li>Custom Chris King components</li>\n<li>Custom Maxxis Forekaster 2.4 EXO tires</li>\n<li>Custom ODI Yeti Speed Grips</li>\n<li>SRAM Motive Ultimate 4p brakes</li>\n<li>FOX Factory Transfer NEO dropper post</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_ASR_Geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_ASR_Geo.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_ASR_Geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_ASR_Geo.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>Adding 10 mm of front travel slightly tweaks the geo of the ASR, resulting in a 66.1º head angle.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Bars.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Bars.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Bars.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Bars.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Trail Ready ASR</h3>\n<p>Shortly after launching the ASR, Yeti had a familiar thought: “What if we put a longer fork on this?” Well, here we are again, the 40th Anniversary ASR is born. With 10mm more travel up front, the head angle gets a bit slacker. Finished with a FOX Float SL, Motive brakes, and Maxxis Forekaster tires, this ASR will be begging for more. Dare it. It’s ready.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Hub.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Hub.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Hub.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Hub.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Front-Hub.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Front-Hub.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Front-Hub.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Front-Hub.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Grip.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Grip.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Grip.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Grip.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Violet Primer</h3>\n<p>Aside from a suspension fork, 24-speeds and bar-ends, nothing was more rad than having your bike tricked out with matching 3D Violet anodized parts. Many shades of anodizing ruled the roost in the 90’s, but it all started with 3D Violet.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Link.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Link.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Link.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Link.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Fox Factory</h3>\n<p>This 40th Anniversary ASR is brought to life with a new benchmark in lightweight, trail-ready performance, the new FOX 34 SL — painted to match with custom silver hardware on both the front and rear suspension.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Seatpost-Collar.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Seatpost-Collar.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Seatpost-Collar.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Seatpost-Collar.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Head-Badge.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Hail to the King, Baby</h3>\n<p>Few brands have been with Yeti since the beginning. A Chris King headset, bottom bracket and seat collar keep things moving smooth and tight, while giving a stylish nod to the glory days.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Der.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Der.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Der.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Rear-Der.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Crank.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Crank.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Crank.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/Yeti_Cycles_40th_ASR__Detail_Crank.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>SRAM</h3>\n<p>Tasteful hits of 3D Violet adorn the one-of-a-kind SRAM XX drivetrain, while the new silver Motive brakes add a vintage flair.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary-4500x6000-2243d33b-b8f2-4e86-af96-05665d8b6d03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary-4500x6000-2243d33b-b8f2-4e86-af96-05665d8b6d03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary-4500x6000-2243d33b-b8f2-4e86-af96-05665d8b6d03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary-4500x6000-2243d33b-b8f2-4e86-af96-05665d8b6d03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Holler at your local <a href=\"https://yeticycles.com/en-us\" target=\"_blank\">Yeti Dealer</a> for more!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/yeti-cycles-40th-anniversary-asr/\">Yeti Cycles Commemorates its 40th Anniversary with a Limited Edition ASR</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ebcb405e734f5c3382cd5eec1c26098ef2d0cc8d907ce5de9fb1a65dd95dfabc","category":"Cycling"}